</header>


<!-- =========================
     SECTION 1   
============================== -->
<section class="section1" id="section1">

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		
		<div class="col-md-6">
			
			<!-- SCREENSHOT -->
			<div class="side-screenshot pull-left">
				<%= image_tag 'planning.jpg', alt: "Feature", class: "img-responsive" %>
			</div>
			
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-md-6">
			
			<!-- DETAILS WITH LIST -->
			<div class="brief text-left">
				
				<!-- HEADING -->
				<h2>The purpose of this service</h2>
				<div class="colored-line pull-left">
				</div>
				
				<!-- TEXT -->
				<p>
					Many local companies, particularly start-ups, are in need of basic, cost effective services involving business and technology. Penn State, like all universities, is home to a broad spectrum of people and organizations with expertise that could be useful to companies on the outside. The Connectme.to website is specifically designed to help link companies to the expertise, skills and resources available within the university in order to promote economic development. 
				</p>
				
				<!-- FEATURE LIST -->
				<ul class="feature-list-2">
					
					<!-- FEATURE -->
					<li>
					<!-- DETAILS -->
					<div class="details pull-left">
						<h6>At present..</h6>
						<p>
							There is no systematic or efficient way for companies to identify resources inside the university. Likewise, there is no systematic or efficient manner for people within the university, including faculty, staff, and students, to advertise their areas of expertise and their interest in providing services to outside companies.
						</p>
					</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div> <!-- /END DETAILS WITH LIST -->
		
	</div> <!-- END ROW -->
	
</div> <!-- END CONTAINER -->

<div class="container">
	
	<div class="row">
		
		<div class="col-md-6">
			
			<!-- DETAILS WITH LIST -->
			<div class="brief text-left">
				
				<!-- HEADING -->
				<h2>For Students and University Faculty &amp; Staff</h2>
				<div class="colored-line pull-left">
				</div>
				
				<!-- TEXT -->
				<p>
					ConnectMeTo allows those in the university wishing to provide services in the form of consulting (volunteer or fee-based), mentoring, class projects, and internships to make these services public. Likewise, Connectme.to will allow companies with specific needs to identify resources at the university to provide assistance.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<!-- SCREENSHOT -->
			<div class="side-screenshot2 pull-right">
				<%= image_tag 'computer.jpg', alt: "Feature", class: "img-responsive" %>
			</div>
		</div>
		
	</div> <!-- END ROW -->
	
</div> <!-- END CONTAINER -->

</section>


